ADDITIONAL ETHICAL USE CLAUSE:

This software is designed for mental health support and analysis. Users and 
contributors are expected to:

1. Use this software responsibly and ethically
2. Not use it as a substitute for professional mental health care
3. Respect user privacy and confidentiality
4. Follow applicable laws and regulations regarding mental health data
5. Prioritize user safety and well-being in all implementations
6. Provide appropriate disclaimers about the limitations of AI-based analysis
7. Include crisis resources and professional referral information

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any 
misuse, misinterpretation, or harm resulting from the use of this software. 
This software is provided for supportive and educational purposes only and 
should not be used for clinical diagnosis or treatment decisions.

For questions about ethical use, please contact the maintainers or refer to 
the project's ethical guidelines in the documentation.
